                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audi</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>Viruni <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Iuni<supplied reason="lost">anus</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>torquib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>umero</ex></expan> II <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="5"/>c<supplied reason="lost">oronis</supplied> mur<supplied reason="lost">alibus III <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXI<supplied reason="lost">I Pr</supplied>imig<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>n<supplied reason="lost">iae</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ilus</ex></expan> princep<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Höhe und Breite nach lupa 9002; rekonstruierbare Breite ca. 215 cm. Unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes drei Mauerkronen. Zwischenzeitlich verschollen und in jüngerer Zeit wiederentdeckt (lupa 9002). (B): CIL 03, 11667: Lesung unvollständig; Jantsch, Carinthia: Grabinschrift: beide Namen zu den Verstorbenen gehörig und im Nominativ aufgelöst; Wedenig: Z. 6: leg(ionis) XXII [Pr]imig[e]n[iae ---].</p>
            </div>
